### Phase 3: Agent API Endpoints

#### [NEW] `app/api/biometric/agent/register/route.ts`

Called by the agent on startup. Registers/updates the agent in `campus_agents`.

- Accepts: `{ collegeId, agentSecret, agentVersion, localIpAddress }`
