- Returns: `{ success: true, agentId }`

#### [NEW] `app/api/biometric/agent/heartbeat/route.ts`

Called every 30 seconds by the agent.

- Updates `lastHeartbeat` and `isOnline` in `campus_agents`
- Returns any pending commands count (optimization: agent can skip polling if count is 0)

#### [NEW] `app/api/biometric/agent/command/route.ts`

The agent's main work loop endpoint.

- `GET`: Fetch next pending command for this college
- `POST`: Submit command result (success or failure)
- Updates `agent_command_queue` status → `completed` or `failed`

